  "title": "Mildly Salty Ethiopian Serrano Ham Gored Gored",
  "description": "A kid-friendly Ethiopian dish featuring serrano ham and a mild salty flavor, this gored gored is a unique twist on traditional recipes. It is kosher-friendly and perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
